title: Xara WebStyle 4.0 Full RIP w/ Templates
description:
This is a full rip of Xara WebStyle 4.0.

It's a RIP of the program files, installed from a ISO file, and i installed extra templates.

Since it is just program files, you need registry patches, which are included.
It's tested and working, with over 1000 templates.
